subject: [HW 06] Q1: Survey
content:
Q1: Survey

Please post all questions you have below concerning Q1: Survey in the follow-ups.

If you are stuck on this question, feel free to read through the follow-up responses to see if you can draw any ideas from them.

threads.question: i'm having a trouble with the survey, after I got the passphrase and entered it into the file, it tells me:  \---redacted the passphrase--

follow-ups.feedback: replace *** PASSPHRASE HERE *** with the actual passphrase but keep the quotes
It worked!! Thank you so much.
